{
  "stem": "18397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 474.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It belonged to the government.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had the first one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had the second.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was six stories.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had six.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had seven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after the war, I took over the-- the first one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took it over for the-- for the [INAUDIBLE] you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew where it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew all the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't take too many Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they liked me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] I mean it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was a hard job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then what-- what was it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was like a year before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, from over there they took us from Vilna down to Poland over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it started, the war started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know-- we didn't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have no radio in the-- in the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you something about the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you want to know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Nothing good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] In the army, they took us over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And right away I something anti-Semitism, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They hate Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was in their-- in their nature, in the blood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So the-- after the first or second day, they wake us up in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The guy, you know, the corporal took him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was to take-- take something from the soldiers, you know, to break him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He thought-- he could break his leg, he says.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a piece of straw like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he could break his leg [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they wake us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] everybody up, you know, in-- in-- had a-- they didn't get no [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Had something wrong with us, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to take brushes and clean the-- the floors, everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
